  <brief_title>Adjuvant Chemotherapy With Paclitaxel and Cisplatin in Lymph Node-Positive Thoracic Esophageal Squamous Cell Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Adjuvant Chemotherapy With Paclitaxel and Cisplatin in Patients With Advanced Esophageal Cancer</official_title>
